// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2626 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f416dc57-4686-5004-8901-4e00950f4b48

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
